11.Name: current_open_wounds
11.SqlCommand:
WITH Current_Open AS (
    SELECT DISTINCT
         wst.woundFk as woundId,
         wst.isCurrentState,
         wstt.name
    FROM rpt.woundstate wst
    INNER JOIN rpt.woundstatetype wstt ON wstt.id=wst.woundStateTypeFk
    INNER JOIN rpt.note n ON n.woundStateFk=wst.id
    WHERE wst.isCurrentState=1
    AND wstt.name='Open'
),

MostRecentEtiologies AS (
    SELECT 
        n.woundFk AS woundId,
        n.patientFk AS patientId,
        n.value AS primaryEtiology,
        ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY n.woundFk ORDER BY n.dimDateFk DESC) AS RowNum
    FROM rpt.Note AS n
    INNER JOIN rpt.AttributeType AS atr ON n.attributeTypeFk = atr.id
    WHERE atr.name = 'Primary Etiology'
    AND n.value IN ('Arterial Ulcer', 'Venous Leg Ulcer/VLU', 
                    'Lower Extremity Diabetic Ulcers (LEDU)/Diabetic Foot Ulcers (DFU)/Diabetic Wounds of the Lower Extremity (DWLE)', 
                    'Pressure Ulcer (PU)/Pressure Injury (PI)')
)

SELECT DISTINCT
  mre.woundId,
  mre.patientId,
  CASE 
     WHEN mre.primaryEtiology='Lower Extremity Diabetic Ulcers (LEDU)/Diabetic Foot Ulcers (DFU)/Diabetic Wounds of the Lower Extremity (DWLE)'  THEN 'Diabetic Ulcer'
     WHEN mre.primaryEtiology='Venous Leg Ulcer/VLU' THEN 'Venous Leg Ulcer'
     WHEN mre.primaryEtiology= 'Pressure Ulcer (PU)/Pressure Injury (PI)' THEN 'Pressure Ulcer'
     ELSE mre.primaryEtiology
   END AS primaryEtiology
FROM MostRecentEtiologies mre
INNER JOIN Current_Open AS co ON co.woundId = mre.woundId
WHERE mre.RowNum=1;

12.Name: current_age_dist
12.SqlCommand:
WITH Current_Open AS (
    SELECT DISTINCT
         wst.woundFk AS woundId
    FROM rpt.woundstate wst
    INNER JOIN rpt.woundstatetype wstt ON wstt.id = wst.woundStateTypeFk
    WHERE wst.isCurrentState = 1
    AND wstt.name = 'Open'
),

AgeBuckets AS ( 
    SELECT '0-9' AS AgeBucket, 0 AS MinAge, 9 AS MaxAge
    UNION ALL SELECT '10-19', 10, 19
    UNION ALL SELECT '20-29', 20, 29
    UNION ALL SELECT '30-39', 30, 39
    UNION ALL SELECT '40-49', 40, 49
    UNION ALL SELECT '50-59', 50, 59
    UNION ALL SELECT '60-69', 60, 69
    UNION ALL SELECT '70-79', 70, 79
    UNION ALL SELECT '80-89', 80, 89
    UNION ALL SELECT '90-99', 90, 99
    UNION ALL SELECT 'after 100', 100, 110
),

MostRecentEtiologies AS (
    SELECT 
        n.value AS PrimaryEtiology,
        n.woundFk,
        ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY n.woundFk ORDER BY n.dimDateFk DESC) AS RowNum
    FROM rpt.Note AS n
    INNER JOIN rpt.AttributeType AS atr ON n.attributeTypeFk = atr.id
    WHERE atr.name = 'Primary Etiology'
    AND n.value IN ('Arterial Ulcer', 'Venous Leg Ulcer/VLU', 
                    'Lower Extremity Diabetic Ulcers (LEDU)/Diabetic Foot Ulcers (DFU)/Diabetic Wounds of the Lower Extremity (DWLE)', 
                    'Pressure Ulcer (PU)/Pressure Injury (PI)')
),

FilteredEtiologies AS (
    SELECT 
        CASE 
            WHEN mre.PrimaryEtiology = 'Lower Extremity Diabetic Ulcers (LEDU)/Diabetic Foot Ulcers (DFU)/Diabetic Wounds of the Lower Extremity (DWLE)' THEN 'Diabetic Ulcer'
            WHEN mre.PrimaryEtiology = 'Venous Leg Ulcer/VLU' THEN 'Venous Leg Ulcer'
            WHEN mre.PrimaryEtiology = 'Pressure Ulcer (PU)/Pressure Injury (PI)' THEN 'Pressure Ulcer'
            ELSE mre.PrimaryEtiology
        END AS PrimaryEtiology,
        mre.woundFk
    FROM MostRecentEtiologies mre
    WHERE mre.RowNum = 1 -- Only the most recent Primary Etiology per wound
),

Ages AS (
    SELECT 
        fe.PrimaryEtiology,
        fe.woundFk,
        w.patientFk,
        DATEDIFF(YEAR, p.dateOfBirth, GETDATE()) - 
            CASE 
                WHEN MONTH(GETDATE()) < MONTH(p.dateOfBirth) OR 
                     (MONTH(GETDATE()) = MONTH(p.dateOfBirth) AND DAY(GETDATE()) < DAY(p.dateOfBirth)) 
                THEN 1 ELSE 0 
            END AS Age
    FROM FilteredEtiologies AS fe
    INNER JOIN Current_Open co ON co.woundId = fe.woundFk
    INNER JOIN rpt.Wound AS w ON w.id = fe.woundFk
    INNER JOIN rpt.Patient AS p ON w.patientFk = p.id
),

AgeCounts AS (
    SELECT 
        PrimaryEtiology,
        CASE 
            WHEN Age BETWEEN 0 AND 9 THEN '0-9'
            WHEN Age BETWEEN 10 AND 19 THEN '10-19'
            WHEN Age BETWEEN 20 AND 29 THEN '20-29'
            WHEN Age BETWEEN 30 AND 39 THEN '30-39'
            WHEN Age BETWEEN 40 AND 49 THEN '40-49'
            WHEN Age BETWEEN 50 AND 59 THEN '50-59'
            WHEN Age BETWEEN 60 AND 69 THEN '60-69'
            WHEN Age BETWEEN 70 AND 79 THEN '70-79'
            WHEN Age BETWEEN 80 AND 89 THEN '80-89'
            WHEN Age BETWEEN 90 AND 99 THEN '90-99'
            ELSE 'after 100' 
        END AS AgeBucket,
        COUNT(*) AS Count
    FROM Ages
    GROUP BY 
        PrimaryEtiology,
        CASE 
            WHEN Age BETWEEN 0 AND 9 THEN '0-9'
            WHEN Age BETWEEN 10 AND 19 THEN '10-19'
            WHEN Age BETWEEN 20 AND 29 THEN '20-29'
            WHEN Age BETWEEN 30 AND 39 THEN '30-39'
            WHEN Age BETWEEN 40 AND 49 THEN '40-49'
            WHEN Age BETWEEN 50 AND 59 THEN '50-59'
            WHEN Age BETWEEN 60 AND 69 THEN '60-69'
            WHEN Age BETWEEN 70 AND 79 THEN '70-79'
            WHEN Age BETWEEN 80 AND 89 THEN '80-89'
            WHEN Age BETWEEN 90 AND 99 THEN '90-99'
            ELSE 'after 100' 
        END
),

DistinctPrimaryEtiologies AS (
    SELECT DISTINCT PrimaryEtiology
    FROM Ages
),

AllCombinations AS (
    SELECT 
        ab.AgeBucket,
        ab.MinAge,
        ab.MaxAge,
        pe.PrimaryEtiology
    FROM AgeBuckets AS ab
    CROSS JOIN DistinctPrimaryEtiologies AS pe
)

SELECT 
    ac.PrimaryEtiology,
    ac.AgeBucket,
    COALESCE(ag.Count, 0) AS Count
FROM AllCombinations ac
LEFT JOIN AgeCounts ag 
    ON ac.AgeBucket = ag.AgeBucket AND ac.PrimaryEtiology = ag.PrimaryEtiology
ORDER BY ac.PrimaryEtiology, ac.MinAge;

13.Name: current_open_wounds_duration
13.SqlCommand:
--Gets all CURRENT open wounds 
WITH OpenWounds AS (
    SELECT 
        w.id AS woundId,
        wst.startDateDimDateFk AS startDateDimDateFk,
        d.date AS startDate
    FROM rpt.Wound AS w
    INNER JOIN rpt.WoundState AS wst ON w.id = wst.woundFk
    INNER JOIN rpt.WoundStateType AS wstt ON wst.woundStateTypeFk = wstt.id
    INNER JOIN rpt.DimDate AS d ON wst.startDateDimDateFk = d.id
    WHERE wst.isCurrentState = 1
      AND wstt.name = 'open'
),

--Gets the woundFk's with a primary etiology of arterial ulcer at any given time
MostRecentEtiologies AS (
    SELECT 
        n.woundFk AS woundId,
        n.value AS primaryEtiology,
        ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY n.woundFk ORDER BY n.dimDateFk DESC) AS RowNum
    FROM rpt.Note AS n
    INNER JOIN rpt.AttributeType AS atr ON n.attributeTypeFk = atr.id
    WHERE atr.name = 'Primary Etiology'
AND n.value IN ('Arterial Ulcer', 'Venous Leg Ulcer/VLU', 'Lower Extremity Diabetic Ulcers (LEDU)/Diabetic Foot Ulcers (DFU)/Diabetic Wounds of the Lower Extremity (DWLE)', 'Pressure Ulcer (PU)/Pressure Injury (PI)')
),

--Gets the woundFk's with most recent primary etiology as arterial ulcer
PrimaryEtiology AS (
    SELECT
        mre.woundId,
        mre.primaryEtiology AS primaryEtiology
    FROM MostRecentEtiologies AS mre
    WHERE mre.RowNum = 1
),

--Gets the difference between the startdate of the 'open' wound state and the current date as months open for all wounds that have a current state of open
WoundDurations AS (
    SELECT 
        ow.woundId,
        ow.startDate,
        DATEDIFF(MONTH, ow.startDate, GETDATE()) AS monthsOpen
    FROM OpenWounds AS ow
)

SELECT 
    wd.woundId,
    wd.startDate,
    wd.monthsOpen,
    CASE
        WHEN wd.monthsOpen BETWEEN 0 AND 3 THEN '0-3 months'
        WHEN wd.monthsOpen BETWEEN 4 AND 6 THEN '3-6 months'
        WHEN wd.monthsOpen BETWEEN 7 AND 9 THEN '6-9 months'
        WHEN wd.monthsOpen BETWEEN 10 AND 12 THEN '9-12 months'
        ELSE 'Over a year'
    END AS timeBracket,
CASE 
            WHEN pe.PrimaryEtiology = 'Lower Extremity Diabetic Ulcers (LEDU)/Diabetic Foot Ulcers (DFU)/Diabetic Wounds of the Lower Extremity (DWLE)' THEN 'Diabetic Ulcer'
            WHEN pe.PrimaryEtiology = 'Venous Leg Ulcer/VLU' THEN 'Venous Leg Ulcer'
            WHEN pe.PrimaryEtiology = 'Pressure Ulcer (PU)/Pressure Injury (PI)' THEN 'Pressure Ulcer'
            WHEN pe.PrimaryEtiology = 'Arterial Ulcer' THEN 'Arterial Ulcer'
            ELSE pe.primaryEtiology
        END AS primaryEtiology
FROM WoundDurations AS wd
INNER JOIN PrimaryEtiology AS pe 
    ON wd.woundId = pe.woundId
ORDER BY timeBracket, wd.woundId;

14.Name: new_wounds
14.SqlCommand:
WITH InitialAssessment AS (
    -- Get the initial (earliest) assessment date for each wound
    SELECT 
        w.id AS woundFk,
        MIN(a.date) AS InitialAssessmentDate
    FROM 
        rpt.wound w
    INNER JOIN 
        rpt.assessment a
        ON w.id = a.woundFk
    GROUP BY 
        w.id
),
PrimaryEtiologies AS (
    -- Get the most recent primary etiology for each wound
    SELECT 
        n.woundFk,
        CASE 
            WHEN n.value = 'Lower Extremity Diabetic Ulcers (LEDU)/Diabetic Foot Ulcers (DFU)/Diabetic Wounds of the Lower Extremity (DWLE)' THEN 'Diabetic'
            WHEN n.value = 'Venous Leg Ulcer/VLU' THEN 'Venous'
            WHEN n.value = 'Pressure Ulcer (PU)/Pressure Injury (PI)' THEN 'Pressure'
            WHEN n.value = 'Arterial Ulcer' THEN 'Arterial'
            ELSE n.value
        END AS primaryEtiology,
        ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY n.woundFk ORDER BY n.dimdatefk DESC) AS RowNum
    FROM 
        rpt.note n
    INNER JOIN 
        rpt.AttributeType atr
        ON n.attributeTypeFk = atr.id
    WHERE 
        atr.name = 'Primary Etiology'
),
OpenWounds AS (
    -- Identify wounds that were open exactly 6 months before the current date
    SELECT 
        w.id AS woundFk
    FROM 
        rpt.wound w
    INNER JOIN 
        rpt.WoundState ws
        ON w.id = ws.woundFk
    WHERE 
        ws.startDateDimDateFk <= DATEADD(MONTH, -6, GETDATE())
        AND (ws.endDateDimDateFk IS NULL OR ws.endDateDimDateFk >= DATEADD(MONTH, -6, GETDATE()))
        AND ws.isCurrentState = 1
        AND ws.woundStateTypeFk IN (
            SELECT id 
            FROM rpt.WoundStateType 
            WHERE name = 'Open'
        )
),
HealedWounds AS (
    SELECT 
        w.id AS woundId,
        wst.startDateDimDateFk AS healedDateDimDateFk,
        d.date AS healedDate,
        ia.InitialAssessmentDate,
        CASE 
            WHEN wstt.name = 'Resurfaced/resolved' THEN 
                DATEDIFF(DAY, ia.InitialAssessmentDate, d.date) -- Calculate days to heal
            ELSE NULL
        END AS DaysToHeal
    FROM rpt.Wound AS w
    INNER JOIN rpt.WoundState AS wst ON w.id = wst.woundFk
    INNER JOIN rpt.WoundStateType AS wstt ON wst.woundStateTypeFk = wstt.id -- Ensure 'wstt.name' is used
    LEFT JOIN rpt.DimDate AS d ON wst.startDateDimDateFk = d.id
    LEFT JOIN InitialAssessment ia ON w.id = ia.woundFk
    WHERE wst.isCurrentState = 1
      AND wstt.name <> 'open'
),
FilteredWounds AS (
    -- Combine data and classify wounds
    SELECT 
        ia.woundFk,
        pe.PrimaryEtiology,
        ia.InitialAssessmentDate,
        CASE 
            WHEN ia.InitialAssessmentDate >= DATEADD(MONTH, -6, GETDATE()) THEN 1
            ELSE NULL
        END AS IsNew,
        CASE 
            WHEN ia.InitialAssessmentDate < DATEADD(MONTH, -6, GETDATE()) AND ow.woundFk IS NOT NULL THEN 1
            ELSE NULL
        END AS IsExisting
    FROM 
        InitialAssessment ia
    LEFT JOIN 
        PrimaryEtiologies pe
        ON ia.woundFk = pe.woundFk AND pe.RowNum = 1
    LEFT JOIN 
        OpenWounds ow
        ON ia.woundFk = ow.woundFk
)
-- Final result: include wounds with either "New" or "Existing" classification and their current state
SELECT 
    fw.woundFk,
    fw.PrimaryEtiology,
    fw.IsNew AS New,         -- 1 if the wound is "New"
    fw.IsExisting AS Existing, -- 1 if the wound is "Already Existing"
    fw.InitialAssessmentDate,
    ws.isCurrentState,
    ws.startDateDimDateFk AS CurrentStateStartDate,
    wstt.name AS CurrentStateName,  -- Corrected column reference
    hw.DaysToHeal,  -- New column for how long it took to heal
    CASE 
        WHEN hw.DaysToHeal IS NOT NULL THEN 
            CASE 
                WHEN hw.DaysToHeal <= 90 THEN 'Before 3 months'
                WHEN hw.DaysToHeal > 90 THEN 'After 3 months'
            END
        ELSE NULL
    END AS StateComparison
FROM 
    FilteredWounds fw
LEFT JOIN 
    rpt.WoundState ws
    ON fw.woundFk = ws.woundFk AND ws.isCurrentState = 1
LEFT JOIN 
    rpt.WoundStateType wstt
    ON ws.woundStateTypeFk = wstt.id
LEFT JOIN 
    HealedWounds hw
    ON fw.woundFk = hw.woundId
WHERE 
    fw.IsNew = 1 OR fw.IsExisting = 1
ORDER BY 
    fw.InitialAssessmentDate;

15.Name: healed_wounds
15.SqlCommand:
WITH InitialAssessment AS (
    -- Get the initial (earliest) assessment date for each wound
    SELECT 
        w.id AS woundFk,
        MIN(a.date) AS InitialAssessmentDate
    FROM 
        rpt.wound w
    INNER JOIN 
        rpt.assessment a
        ON w.id = a.woundFk

),
PrimaryEtiologies AS (

       CASE

            WHEN n.value = 'Venous Leg Ulcer/VLU' THEN 'Venous'
            WHEN n.value = 'Pressure Ulcer (PU)/Pressure Injury (PI)' THEN 'Pressure'

        END AS primaryEtiology,

    FROM 
        rpt.note n
    INNER JOIN 
        rpt.AttributeType atr
        ON n.attributeTypeFk = atr.id
    WHERE 
        atr.name = 'Primary Etiology'
),
OpenWounds AS (
    -- Identify wounds that were open exactly 6 months before the current date
    SELECT 
        w.id AS woundFk
    FROM 
        rpt.wound w
    INNER JOIN 
        rpt.WoundState ws
        ON w.id = ws.woundFk
    WHERE 
        ws.startDateDimDateFk <= DATEADD(MONTH, -6, GETDATE())
        AND (ws.endDateDimDateFk IS NULL OR ws.endDateDimDateFk >= DATEADD(MONTH, -6, GETDATE()))
        AND ws.isCurrentState = 1
        AND ws.woundStateTypeFk IN (
            SELECT id 
            FROM rpt.WoundStateType 
            WHERE name = 'Open'
        )
),
HealedWounds AS (
    SELECT 
        w.id AS woundId,
        wst.startDateDimDateFk AS healedDateDimDateFk,
        d.date AS healedDate,
        ia.InitialAssessmentDate,
        CASE 
            WHEN wstt.name = 'Resurfaced/resolved' THEN 
                DATEDIFF(DAY, ia.InitialAssessmentDate, d.date) -- Calculate days to heal
            ELSE NULL
        END AS DaysToHeal
    FROM rpt.Wound AS w
    INNER JOIN rpt.WoundState AS wst ON w.id = wst.woundFk
    INNER JOIN rpt.WoundStateType AS wstt ON wst.woundStateTypeFk = wstt.id -- Ensure 'wstt.name' is used
    LEFT JOIN rpt.DimDate AS d ON wst.startDateDimDateFk = d.id
    LEFT JOIN InitialAssessment ia ON w.id = ia.woundFk
    WHERE wst.isCurrentState = 1
      AND wstt.name <> 'open'
),
FilteredWounds AS (
    -- Combine data and classify wounds
    SELECT 
        ia.woundFk,
        pe.PrimaryEtiology,
        ia.InitialAssessmentDate,
        CASE 
            WHEN ia.InitialAssessmentDate >= DATEADD(MONTH, -6, GETDATE()) THEN 1
            ELSE NULL
        END AS IsNew,
        CASE 
            WHEN ia.InitialAssessmentDate < DATEADD(MONTH, -6, GETDATE()) AND ow.woundFk IS NOT NULL THEN 1
            ELSE NULL
        END AS IsExisting
    FROM 
        InitialAssessment ia
    LEFT JOIN 
        PrimaryEtiologies pe
        ON ia.woundFk = pe.woundFk AND pe.RowNum = 1
    LEFT JOIN 
        OpenWounds ow
        ON ia.woundFk = ow.woundFk
),
-- Final result: include wounds with either "New" or "Existing" classification and their current state
FINAL AS (
    SELECT 
        fw.woundFk,
        fw.PrimaryEtiology,
        fw.IsNew AS New,         -- 1 if the wound is "New"
        fw.IsExisting AS Existing, -- 1 if the wound is "Already Existing"
        fw.InitialAssessmentDate,
        ws.isCurrentState,
        ws.startDateDimDateFk AS CurrentStateStartDate,
        wstt.name AS CurrentStateName,  -- Corrected column reference
        hw.DaysToHeal,  -- New column for how long it took to heal
        CASE 
            WHEN hw.DaysToHeal IS NOT NULL THEN 
                CASE 
                    WHEN hw.DaysToHeal <= 90 THEN 'Before 3 months'
                    WHEN hw.DaysToHeal > 90 THEN 'After 3 months'
                END
            ELSE NULL
        END AS StateComparison
    FROM 
        FilteredWounds fw
    LEFT JOIN 
        rpt.WoundState ws
        ON fw.woundFk = ws.woundFk AND ws.isCurrentState = 1
    LEFT JOIN 
        rpt.WoundStateType wstt
        ON ws.woundStateTypeFk = wstt.id
    LEFT JOIN 
        HealedWounds hw
        ON fw.woundFk = hw.woundId
    WHERE 
        fw.IsNew = 1 OR fw.IsExisting = 1
)
SELECT * 
FROM FINAL f 
WHERE f.StateComparison IS NOT NULL
ORDER BY f.woundFk;

16.Name: open_wounds
16.SqlCommand:
WITH InitialAssessment AS (
    -- Get the initial (earliest) assessment date for each wound
    SELECT 
        w.id AS woundFk,
        MIN(a.date) AS InitialAssessmentDate
    FROM 
        rpt.wound w
    INNER JOIN 
        rpt.assessment a
        ON w.id = a.woundFk
    GROUP BY 
        w.id
),

RankedMeasurements AS (
    -- Rank measurements for each wound by proximity to the current date
    SELECT 
        m.woundFk,
        m.volume,
        m.dimDateFk,
        ROW_NUMBER() OVER (
            PARTITION BY m.woundFk 
            ORDER BY ABS(DATEDIFF(DAY, GETDATE(), d.date)) ASC
        ) AS MeasurementRank,
        ROW_NUMBER() OVER (
            PARTITION BY m.woundFk 
            ORDER BY d.date ASC
        ) AS InitialRank
    FROM rpt.Measurement AS m
    INNER JOIN rpt.DimDate AS d ON m.dimDateFk = d.id
),

FilteredWounds AS (
    -- Determine if a wound is new or existing
    SELECT DISTINCT
        w.id AS woundFk,
        w.patientFk AS patientFk,
        ia.InitialAssessmentDate,
        CASE 
            WHEN ia.InitialAssessmentDate >= DATEADD(MONTH, -6, GETDATE()) THEN 1
            ELSE 0
        END AS IsNew,
        CASE 
            WHEN ia.InitialAssessmentDate < DATEADD(MONTH, -6, GETDATE()) THEN 1
            ELSE 0
        END AS IsExisting
    FROM rpt.Wound w
    LEFT JOIN InitialAssessment ia ON ia.woundFk = w.id
),

FinalResults AS (
    -- Combine all data into the final result
    SELECT 
        fw.woundFk AS wound,
        (SELECT TOP 1 n.value
         FROM rpt.Note n
         INNER JOIN rpt.AttributeType atr 
         ON n.attributeTypeFk = atr.id
         WHERE n.woundFk = fw.woundFk 
           AND atr.name = 'Primary Etiology'
         ORDER BY n.dimDateFk DESC) AS primaryEtiology,
        fw.patientFk AS patient,
        fw.IsExisting,
        fw.IsNew,
        im.volume AS initialMeasurement,
        im.dimDateFk AS initialMeasurementDate,
        cm.volume AS closestMeasurement,
        cm.dimDateFk AS closestMeasurementDate,
        CASE 
            WHEN im.volume > 0 THEN (cm.volume / im.volume) * 100
            ELSE 0
        END AS percentChange,
        CASE
            WHEN (cm.volume / im.volume) * 100 <= 50 THEN 'Decreased by > 50%'
            WHEN (cm.volume / im.volume) * 100 > 50 AND (cm.volume / im.volume) * 100 <= 100 THEN 'Decreased by < 50%'
            WHEN (cm.volume / im.volume) * 100 > 100 THEN 'Increased'
            ELSE 'Unknown'
        END AS percentBucket
    FROM FilteredWounds fw
    LEFT JOIN RankedMeasurements im 
        ON fw.woundFk = im.woundFk AND im.InitialRank = 1 -- Initial measurement
    LEFT JOIN RankedMeasurements cm 
        ON fw.woundFk = cm.woundFk AND cm.MeasurementRank = 1 -- Closest measurement
    WHERE im.volume IS NOT NULL 
      AND cm.volume IS NOT NULL
      AND im.dimDateFk <> cm.dimDateFk -- Exclude wounds where the dates are the same
)

SELECT 
    wound,
    CASE 
            WHEN primaryEtiology= 'Lower Extremity Diabetic Ulcers (LEDU)/Diabetic Foot Ulcers (DFU)/Diabetic Wounds of the Lower Extremity (DWLE)' THEN 'Diabetic'
            WHEN primaryEtiology= 'Venous Leg Ulcer/VLU' THEN 'Venous'
            WHEN primaryEtiology= 'Pressure Ulcer (PU)/Pressure Injury (PI)' THEN 'Pressure'
            WHEN primaryEtiology= 'Arterial Ulcer' THEN 'Arterial'
            ELSE primaryEtiology
        END AS primaryEtiology,
    patient,
    IsExisting,
    IsNew,
    initialMeasurement,
    initialMeasurementDate,
    closestMeasurement,
    closestMeasurementDate,
    percentChange,
    percentBucket
FROM FinalResults
WHERE initialMeasurementDate <> closestMeasurementDate -- Final check for date mismatch
ORDER BY wound;

17.Name: pressure_initial
17.SqlCommand:
WITH InitialAssessment AS (
    -- Get the initial (earliest) assessment date for each wound
    SELECT 
        w.id AS woundFk,
        MIN(a.date) AS InitialAssessmentDate
    FROM 
        rpt.wound w
    INNER JOIN 
        rpt.assessment a ON w.id = a.woundFk
    GROUP BY 
        w.id
),

RankedWoundStates AS (
    SELECT 
        n.value AS value,
        n.woundFk AS wound,
        CASE 
            WHEN n.value = 'Lower Extremity Diabetic Ulcers (LEDU)/Diabetic Foot Ulcers (DFU)/Diabetic Wounds of the Lower Extremity (DWLE)' THEN 'Diabetic'
            WHEN n.value = 'Venous Leg Ulcer/VLU' THEN 'Venous'
            WHEN n.value = 'Pressure Ulcer (PU)/Pressure Injury (PI)' THEN 'Pressure'
            WHEN n.value = 'Arterial Ulcer' THEN 'Arterial'
            ELSE n.value
        END AS primaryEtiology
    FROM rpt.Note AS n
    INNER JOIN rpt.AttributeType AS atr ON n.attributeTypeFk = atr.id
    WHERE atr.name = 'Primary Etiology'
      AND n.dimDateFk = (
          SELECT MAX(n2.dimDateFk)
          FROM rpt.Note AS n2
          INNER JOIN rpt.AttributeType AS atr2 ON n2.attributeTypeFk = atr2.id
          WHERE n2.woundFk = n.woundFk
            AND atr2.name = 'Primary Etiology'
            AND n2.value IN ('Arterial Ulcer', 'Venous Leg Ulcer/VLU', 'Lower Extremity Diabetic Ulcers (LEDU)/Diabetic Foot Ulcers (DFU)/Diabetic Wounds of the Lower Extremity (DWLE)', 'Pressure Ulcer (PU)/Pressure Injury (PI)')
      )
),

FilteredWounds AS (
    SELECT DISTINCT
        rw.wound,
        rw.primaryEtiology,
        CASE 
            WHEN ia.InitialAssessmentDate >= DATEADD(MONTH, -6, GETDATE()) THEN 1
            ELSE 0
        END AS IsNew,
        CASE 
            WHEN ia.InitialAssessmentDate < DATEADD(MONTH, -6, GETDATE()) THEN 1
            ELSE 0
        END AS IsExisting
    FROM RankedWoundStates rw
    LEFT JOIN InitialAssessment ia ON ia.woundFk = rw.wound
),

DateSortedStages AS (
    SELECT 
        w.id AS woundFk,
        atr.name AS AttributeName,
        n.dimdatefk AS Date,
        CASE
            WHEN n.value LIKE '%Stage 1%' THEN 'Stage 1'
            WHEN n.value LIKE '%Stage 2%' THEN 'Stage 2'
            WHEN n.value LIKE '%Stage 3%' THEN 'Stage 3'
            WHEN n.value LIKE '%Stage 4%' THEN 'Stage 4'
            WHEN n.value LIKE '%Unstageable due to Slough%' THEN 'Unstageable'
            WHEN n.value LIKE '%Unstageable due to Deep Tissue%' THEN 'Suspected Deep Tissue Injury'
            ELSE NULL
        END AS AssociatedValue
    FROM rpt.Note n
    INNER JOIN rpt.AttributeType atr
        ON n.attributeTypeFk = atr.id
    INNER JOIN rpt.Wound w
        ON n.woundFk = w.id
    WHERE atr.name = 'Pressure Injury/Pressure Ulcer'
),

FilteredPressureStages AS (
    SELECT 
        ds.woundFk,
        ds.AssociatedValue AS StageValue,
        ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY ds.woundFk ORDER BY ds.Date ASC) AS MinStageRowNum,  -- Row number for minimum (earliest) stage
        ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY ds.woundFk ORDER BY ds.Date DESC) AS MaxStageRowNum  -- Row number for maximum (most recent) stage
    FROM DateSortedStages ds
    INNER JOIN FilteredWounds fw
        ON ds.woundFk = fw.wound
    WHERE (fw.IsNew = 1 OR fw.IsExisting = 1) -- Include only new or existing wounds
      AND ds.AssociatedValue IS NOT NULL  -- Exclude 'other' values or NULL stages
),

WoundCurrentState AS (
    SELECT
        ws.woundFk,
        wst.name AS currentState  -- Get the current state from the woundstatetype table
    FROM rpt.woundstate ws
    INNER JOIN rpt.woundstatetype wst
        ON ws.woundstatetypefk = wst.id
    WHERE ws.isCurrentState = 1  -- Only consider the current wound state
)

SELECT 
    fw.wound AS woundFk,
    fw.primaryEtiology,
    fw.IsNew,
    fw.IsExisting,
    MIN(fps.StageValue) AS minimumStage,  -- Get the minimum (earliest) stage
    CASE
        WHEN wcs.currentState = 'Resurfaced/resolved' THEN 'Resurfaced/resolved'  -- Check if wound state is 'resurfaced/resolved'
        ELSE MAX(fps.StageValue)   -- Otherwise, get the maximum (most recent) stage
    END AS maximumStage  -- Get the maximum (most recent) stage or 'Resurfaced/Resolved'
FROM FilteredWounds fw
LEFT JOIN FilteredPressureStages fps 
    ON fw.wound = fps.woundFk
LEFT JOIN WoundCurrentState wcs
    ON fw.wound = wcs.woundFk  -- Join with current state
WHERE fw.primaryEtiology = 'Pressure'
AND fps.StageValue IS NOT NULL
GROUP BY fw.wound, fw.primaryEtiology, fw.IsNew, fw.IsExisting, wcs.currentState
ORDER BY fw.wound;

18.Name: pressure_age_dist
18.SqlCommand:
WITH AgeBuckets AS (
    SELECT '0-9' AS AgeBucket, 0 AS MinAge, 9 AS MaxAge
    UNION ALL SELECT '10-19', 10, 19
    UNION ALL SELECT '20-29', 20, 29
    UNION ALL SELECT '30-39', 30, 39
    UNION ALL SELECT '40-49', 40, 49
    UNION ALL SELECT '50-59', 50, 59
    UNION ALL SELECT '60-69', 60, 69
    UNION ALL SELECT '70-79', 70, 79
    UNION ALL SELECT '80-89', 80, 89
    UNION ALL SELECT '90-99', 90, 99
    UNION ALL SELECT 'after 100', 100, 110
),
InitialAssessment AS (
    SELECT 
        w.id AS woundFk,
        MIN(a.date) AS InitialAssessmentDate
    FROM 
        rpt.Wound w
    INNER JOIN 
        rpt.Assessment a ON w.id = a.woundFk
    GROUP BY 
        w.id
),
PrimaryEtiologies AS (
    SELECT 
        n.woundFk,
        CASE 
            WHEN n.value = 'Lower Extremity Diabetic Ulcers (LEDU)/Diabetic Foot Ulcers (DFU)/Diabetic Wounds of the Lower Extremity (DWLE)' THEN 'Diabetic'
            WHEN n.value = 'Venous Leg Ulcer/VLU' THEN 'Venous'
            WHEN n.value = 'Pressure Ulcer (PU)/Pressure Injury (PI)' THEN 'Pressure'
            WHEN n.value = 'Arterial Ulcer' THEN 'Arterial'
            ELSE n.value
        END AS PrimaryEtiology,
        ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY n.woundFk ORDER BY n.dimDateFk DESC) AS RowNum
    FROM 
        rpt.Note n
    INNER JOIN 
        rpt.AttributeType atr ON n.attributeTypeFk = atr.id
    WHERE 
        atr.name = 'Primary Etiology'
),
FilteredWounds AS (
    SELECT 
        ia.woundFk,
        pe.PrimaryEtiology,
        ia.InitialAssessmentDate,
        CASE 
            WHEN ia.InitialAssessmentDate >= DATEADD(MONTH, -6, GETDATE()) THEN 1
            ELSE NULL
        END AS IsNew,
        CASE 
            WHEN ia.InitialAssessmentDate < DATEADD(MONTH, -6, GETDATE()) THEN 1
            ELSE NULL
        END AS IsExisting
    FROM 
        InitialAssessment ia
    LEFT JOIN 
        PrimaryEtiologies pe ON ia.woundFk = pe.woundFk AND pe.RowNum = 1
),
PatientAges AS (
    SELECT 
        fw.woundFk,
        fw.PrimaryEtiology,
        DATEDIFF(YEAR, p.dateOfBirth, GETDATE()) - 
            CASE 
                WHEN MONTH(GETDATE()) < MONTH(p.dateOfBirth) OR 
                     (MONTH(GETDATE()) = MONTH(p.dateOfBirth) AND DAY(GETDATE()) < DAY(p.dateOfBirth)) 
                THEN 1 ELSE 0 
            END AS Age
    FROM 
        FilteredWounds fw
    INNER JOIN 
        rpt.Wound w ON fw.woundFk = w.id
    INNER JOIN 
        rpt.Patient p ON w.patientFk = p.id
),
AgeCounts AS (
    SELECT 
        pa.PrimaryEtiology,
        CASE 
            WHEN pa.Age BETWEEN 0 AND 9 THEN '0-9'
            WHEN pa.Age BETWEEN 10 AND 19 THEN '10-19'
            WHEN pa.Age BETWEEN 20 AND 29 THEN '20-29'
            WHEN pa.Age BETWEEN 30 AND 39 THEN '30-39'
            WHEN pa.Age BETWEEN 40 AND 49 THEN '40-49'
            WHEN pa.Age BETWEEN 50 AND 59 THEN '50-59'
            WHEN pa.Age BETWEEN 60 AND 69 THEN '60-69'
            WHEN pa.Age BETWEEN 70 AND 79 THEN '70-79'
            WHEN pa.Age BETWEEN 80 AND 89 THEN '80-89'
            WHEN pa.Age BETWEEN 90 AND 99 THEN '90-99'
            ELSE 'after 100' 
        END AS AgeBucket,
        COUNT(*) AS AgeCount
    FROM 
        PatientAges pa
    GROUP BY 
        pa.PrimaryEtiology,
        CASE 
            WHEN pa.Age BETWEEN 0 AND 9 THEN '0-9'
            WHEN pa.Age BETWEEN 10 AND 19 THEN '10-19'
            WHEN pa.Age BETWEEN 20 AND 29 THEN '20-29'
            WHEN pa.Age BETWEEN 30 AND 39 THEN '30-39'
            WHEN pa.Age BETWEEN 40 AND 49 THEN '40-49'
            WHEN pa.Age BETWEEN 50 AND 59 THEN '50-59'
            WHEN pa.Age BETWEEN 60 AND 69 THEN '60-69'
            WHEN pa.Age BETWEEN 70 AND 79 THEN '70-79'
            WHEN pa.Age BETWEEN 80 AND 89 THEN '80-89'
            WHEN pa.Age BETWEEN 90 AND 99 THEN '90-99'
            ELSE 'after 100' 
        END
),
AllCombinations AS (
    SELECT DISTINCT
        ab.AgeBucket,
        ab.MinAge,
        ab.MaxAge,
        fw.PrimaryEtiology
    FROM 
        AgeBuckets ab
    CROSS JOIN 
        FilteredWounds fw
)
SELECT 
    ac.PrimaryEtiology,
    ac.AgeBucket,
    COALESCE(ag.AgeCount, 0) AS AgeCount
FROM 
    AllCombinations ac
LEFT JOIN 
    AgeCounts ag ON ac.AgeBucket = ag.AgeBucket AND ac.PrimaryEtiology = ag.PrimaryEtiology
WHERE ac.PrimaryEtiology='Pressure'
ORDER BY 
    ac.PrimaryEtiology, ac.MinAge;

19.Name: open_wounds_pressure
19.SqlCommand:
WITH InitialAssessment AS (
    -- Get the initial (earliest) assessment date for each wound
    SELECT 
        w.id AS woundFk,
        MIN(a.date) AS InitialAssessmentDate
    FROM 
        rpt.wound w
    INNER JOIN 
        rpt.assessment a
        ON w.id = a.woundFk
    GROUP BY 
        w.id
),

RankedMeasurements AS (
    -- Rank measurements for each wound by proximity to the current date
    SELECT 
        m.woundFk,
        m.volume,
        m.dimDateFk,
        ROW_NUMBER() OVER (
            PARTITION BY m.woundFk 
            ORDER BY ABS(DATEDIFF(DAY, GETDATE(), d.date)) ASC
        ) AS MeasurementRank,
        ROW_NUMBER() OVER (
            PARTITION BY m.woundFk 
            ORDER BY d.date ASC
        ) AS InitialRank
    FROM rpt.Measurement AS m
    INNER JOIN rpt.DimDate AS d ON m.dimDateFk = d.id
),

FilteredWounds AS (
    -- Determine if a wound is new or existing
    SELECT DISTINCT
        w.id AS woundFk,
        w.patientFk AS patientFk,
        ia.InitialAssessmentDate,
        CASE 
            WHEN ia.InitialAssessmentDate >= DATEADD(MONTH, -6, GETDATE()) THEN 1
            ELSE 0
        END AS IsNew,
        CASE 
            WHEN ia.InitialAssessmentDate < DATEADD(MONTH, -6, GETDATE()) THEN 1
            ELSE 0
        END AS IsExisting
    FROM rpt.Wound w
    LEFT JOIN InitialAssessment ia ON ia.woundFk = w.id
),

FinalResults AS (
    -- Combine all data into the final result
    SELECT 
        fw.woundFk AS wound,
        (SELECT TOP 1 n.value
         FROM rpt.Note n
         INNER JOIN rpt.AttributeType atr 
         ON n.attributeTypeFk = atr.id
         WHERE n.woundFk = fw.woundFk 
           AND atr.name = 'Primary Etiology'
         ORDER BY n.dimDateFk DESC) AS primaryEtiology,
        fw.patientFk AS patient,
        fw.IsExisting,
        fw.IsNew,
        im.volume AS initialMeasurement,
        im.dimDateFk AS initialMeasurementDate,
        cm.volume AS closestMeasurement,
        cm.dimDateFk AS closestMeasurementDate,
        CASE 
            WHEN im.volume > 0 THEN (cm.volume / im.volume) * 100
            ELSE 0
        END AS percentChange,
        CASE
            WHEN (cm.volume / im.volume) * 100 <= 50 THEN 'Decreased by > 50%'
            WHEN (cm.volume / im.volume) * 100 > 50 AND (cm.volume / im.volume) * 100 <= 100 THEN 'Decreased by < 50%'
            WHEN (cm.volume / im.volume) * 100 > 100 THEN 'Increased'
            ELSE 'Unknown'
        END AS percentBucket
    FROM FilteredWounds fw
    LEFT JOIN RankedMeasurements im 
        ON fw.woundFk = im.woundFk AND im.InitialRank = 1 -- Initial measurement
    LEFT JOIN RankedMeasurements cm 
        ON fw.woundFk = cm.woundFk AND cm.MeasurementRank = 1 -- Closest measurement
    WHERE im.volume IS NOT NULL 
      AND cm.volume IS NOT NULL
      AND im.dimDateFk <> cm.dimDateFk -- Exclude wounds where the dates are the same
),

RankedWoundStates AS (
    SELECT 
        n.value AS value,
        n.woundFk AS wound,
        CASE 
            WHEN n.value = 'Lower Extremity Diabetic Ulcers (LEDU)/Diabetic Foot Ulcers (DFU)/Diabetic Wounds of the Lower Extremity (DWLE)' THEN 'Diabetic'
            WHEN n.value = 'Venous Leg Ulcer/VLU' THEN 'Venous'
            WHEN n.value = 'Pressure Ulcer (PU)/Pressure Injury (PI)' THEN 'Pressure'
            WHEN n.value = 'Arterial Ulcer' THEN 'Arterial'
            ELSE n.value
        END AS primaryEtiology
    FROM rpt.Note AS n
    INNER JOIN rpt.AttributeType AS atr ON n.attributeTypeFk = atr.id
    WHERE atr.name = 'Primary Etiology'
      AND n.dimDateFk = (
          SELECT MAX(n2.dimDateFk)
          FROM rpt.Note AS n2
          INNER JOIN rpt.AttributeType AS atr2 ON n2.attributeTypeFk = atr2.id
          WHERE n2.woundFk = n.woundFk
            AND atr2.name = 'Primary Etiology'
            AND n2.value IN ('Arterial Ulcer', 'Venous Leg Ulcer/VLU', 'Lower Extremity Diabetic Ulcers (LEDU)/Diabetic Foot Ulcers (DFU)/Diabetic Wounds of the Lower Extremity (DWLE)', 'Pressure Ulcer (PU)/Pressure Injury (PI)')
      )
),

FilteredWoundsStates AS (
    SELECT DISTINCT
        rw.wound,
        rw.primaryEtiology,
        CASE 
            WHEN ia.InitialAssessmentDate >= DATEADD(MONTH, -6, GETDATE()) THEN 1
            ELSE 0
        END AS IsNew,
        CASE 
            WHEN ia.InitialAssessmentDate < DATEADD(MONTH, -6, GETDATE()) THEN 1
            ELSE 0
        END AS IsExisting
    FROM RankedWoundStates rw
    LEFT JOIN InitialAssessment ia ON ia.woundFk = rw.wound
),

DateSortedStages AS (
    SELECT 
        w.id AS woundFk,
        atr.name AS AttributeName,
        n.dimdatefk AS Date,
        CASE
            WHEN n.value LIKE '%Stage 1%' THEN 'Stage 1'
            WHEN n.value LIKE '%Stage 2%' THEN 'Stage 2'
            WHEN n.value LIKE '%Stage 3%' THEN 'Stage 3'
            WHEN n.value LIKE '%Stage 4%' THEN 'Stage 4'
            WHEN n.value LIKE '%Unstageable due to Slough%' THEN 'Unstageable'
            WHEN n.value LIKE '%Unstageable due to Deep Tissue%' THEN 'Suspected Deep Tissue Injury'
            ELSE NULL
        END AS AssociatedValue
    FROM rpt.Note n
    INNER JOIN rpt.AttributeType atr
        ON n.attributeTypeFk = atr.id
    INNER JOIN rpt.Wound w
        ON n.woundFk = w.id
    WHERE atr.name = 'Pressure Injury/Pressure Ulcer'
),

FilteredPressureStages AS (
    SELECT 
        ds.woundFk,
        ds.AssociatedValue AS StageValue,
        ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY ds.woundFk ORDER BY ds.Date ASC) AS MinStageRowNum,  -- Row number for minimum (earliest) stage
        ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY ds.woundFk ORDER BY ds.Date DESC) AS MaxStageRowNum  -- Row number for maximum (most recent) stage
    FROM DateSortedStages ds
    INNER JOIN FilteredWoundsStates fw
        ON ds.woundFk = fw.wound
    WHERE (fw.IsNew = 1 OR fw.IsExisting = 1) -- Include only new or existing wounds
      AND ds.AssociatedValue IS NOT NULL  -- Exclude 'other' values or NULL stages
),

WoundCurrentState AS (
    SELECT
        ws.woundFk,
        wst.name AS currentState  -- Get the current state from the woundstatetype table
    FROM rpt.woundstate ws
    INNER JOIN rpt.woundstatetype wst
        ON ws.woundstatetypefk = wst.id
    WHERE ws.isCurrentState = 1  -- Only consider the current wound state
)

SELECT 
    fr.wound,
    CASE 
        WHEN fr.primaryEtiology = 'Lower Extremity Diabetic Ulcers (LEDU)/Diabetic Foot Ulcers (DFU)/Diabetic Wounds of the Lower Extremity (DWLE)' THEN 'Diabetic'
        WHEN fr.primaryEtiology = 'Venous Leg Ulcer/VLU' THEN 'Venous'
        WHEN fr.primaryEtiology = 'Pressure Ulcer (PU)/Pressure Injury (PI)' THEN 'Pressure'
        WHEN fr.primaryEtiology = 'Arterial Ulcer' THEN 'Arterial'
        ELSE fr.primaryEtiology
    END AS primaryEtiology,
    fr.patient,
    fr.IsExisting,
    fr.IsNew,
    fr.initialMeasurement,
    fr.initialMeasurementDate,
    fr.closestMeasurement,
    fr.closestMeasurementDate,
    fr.percentChange,
    fr.percentBucket,
    MIN(fps.StageValue) AS initialStage  -- Get the initial stage
FROM FinalResults fr
LEFT JOIN FilteredPressureStages fps 
    ON fr.wound = fps.woundFk
LEFT JOIN WoundCurrentState wcs
    ON fr.wound = wcs.woundFk  -- Join with current state
WHERE fr.primaryEtiology = 'Pressure Ulcer (PU)/Pressure Injury (PI)'
GROUP BY fr.wound, fr.primaryEtiology, fr.patient, fr.IsExisting, fr.IsNew, fr.initialMeasurement, fr.initialMeasurementDate, fr.closestMeasurement, fr.closestMeasurementDate, fr.percentChange, fr.percentBucket
ORDER BY fr.wound;

20.Name: healed_wounds_pressure
20.SqlCommand:
WITH InitialAssessment AS (
    -- Get the initial (earliest) assessment date for each wound
    SELECT 
        w.id AS woundFk,
        MIN(a.date) AS InitialAssessmentDate
    FROM 
        rpt.wound w
    INNER JOIN 
        rpt.assessment a
        ON w.id = a.woundFk
    GROUP BY 
        w.id
),
PrimaryEtiologies AS (
    -- Get the most recent primary etiology for each wound
    SELECT 
        n.woundFk,
        CASE 
            WHEN n.value = 'Lower Extremity Diabetic Ulcers (LEDU)/Diabetic Foot Ulcers (DFU)/Diabetic Wounds of the Lower Extremity (DWLE)' THEN 'Diabetic'
            WHEN n.value = 'Venous Leg Ulcer/VLU' THEN 'Venous'
            WHEN n.value = 'Pressure Ulcer (PU)/Pressure Injury (PI)' THEN 'Pressure'
            WHEN n.value = 'Arterial Ulcer' THEN 'Arterial'
            ELSE n.value
        END AS primaryEtiology,
        ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY n.woundFk ORDER BY n.dimdatefk DESC) AS RowNum
    FROM 
        rpt.note n
    INNER JOIN 
        rpt.AttributeType atr
        ON n.attributeTypeFk = atr.id
    WHERE 
        atr.name = 'Primary Etiology'
),
OpenWounds AS (
    -- Identify wounds that were open exactly 6 months before the current date
    SELECT 
        w.id AS woundFk
    FROM 
        rpt.wound w
    INNER JOIN 
        rpt.WoundState ws
        ON w.id = ws.woundFk
    WHERE 
        ws.startDateDimDateFk <= DATEADD(MONTH, -6, GETDATE())
        AND (ws.endDateDimDateFk IS NULL OR ws.endDateDimDateFk >= DATEADD(MONTH, -6, GETDATE()))
        AND ws.isCurrentState = 1
        AND ws.woundStateTypeFk IN (
            SELECT id 
            FROM rpt.WoundStateType 
            WHERE name = 'Open'
        )
),
HealedWounds AS (
    SELECT 
        w.id AS woundId,
        wst.startDateDimDateFk AS healedDateDimDateFk,
        d.date AS healedDate,
        ia.InitialAssessmentDate,
        CASE 
            WHEN wstt.name = 'Resurfaced/resolved' THEN 
                DATEDIFF(DAY, ia.InitialAssessmentDate, d.date) -- Calculate days to heal
            ELSE NULL
        END AS DaysToHeal
    FROM rpt.Wound AS w
    INNER JOIN rpt.WoundState AS wst ON w.id = wst.woundFk
    INNER JOIN rpt.WoundStateType AS wstt ON wst.woundStateTypeFk = wstt.id -- Ensure 'wstt.name' is used
    LEFT JOIN rpt.DimDate AS d ON wst.startDateDimDateFk = d.id
    LEFT JOIN InitialAssessment ia ON w.id = ia.woundFk
    WHERE wst.isCurrentState = 1
      AND wstt.name <> 'open'
),
FilteredWounds AS (
    -- Combine data and classify wounds
    SELECT 
        ia.woundFk,
        pe.PrimaryEtiology,
        ia.InitialAssessmentDate,
        CASE 
            WHEN ia.InitialAssessmentDate >= DATEADD(MONTH, -6, GETDATE()) THEN 1
            ELSE NULL
        END AS IsNew,
        CASE 
            WHEN ia.InitialAssessmentDate < DATEADD(MONTH, -6, GETDATE()) AND ow.woundFk IS NOT NULL THEN 1
            ELSE NULL
        END AS IsExisting
    FROM 
        InitialAssessment ia
    LEFT JOIN 
        PrimaryEtiologies pe
        ON ia.woundFk = pe.woundFk AND pe.RowNum = 1
    LEFT JOIN 
        OpenWounds ow
        ON ia.woundFk = ow.woundFk
),
DateSortedStages AS (
    SELECT 
        w.id AS woundFk,
        atr.name AS AttributeName,
        n.dimdatefk AS Date,
        CASE
            WHEN n.value LIKE '%Stage 1%' THEN 'Stage 1'
            WHEN n.value LIKE '%Stage 2%' THEN 'Stage 2'
            WHEN n.value LIKE '%Stage 3%' THEN 'Stage 3'
            WHEN n.value LIKE '%Stage 4%' THEN 'Stage 4'
            WHEN n.value LIKE '%Unstageable due to Slough%' THEN 'Unstageable'
            WHEN n.value LIKE '%Unstageable due to Deep Tissue%' THEN 'Suspected Deep Tissue Injury'
            ELSE NULL
        END AS AssociatedValue
    FROM rpt.Note n
    INNER JOIN rpt.AttributeType atr
        ON n.attributeTypeFk = atr.id
    INNER JOIN rpt.Wound w
        ON n.woundFk = w.id
    WHERE atr.name = 'Pressure Injury/Pressure Ulcer'
),
FilteredPressureStages AS (
    SELECT 
        ds.woundFk,
        ds.AssociatedValue AS StageValue,
        ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY ds.woundFk ORDER BY ds.Date ASC) AS MinStageRowNum  -- Row number for minimum (earliest) stage
    FROM DateSortedStages ds
    INNER JOIN FilteredWounds fw
        ON ds.woundFk = fw.woundFk
    WHERE ds.AssociatedValue IS NOT NULL  -- Exclude 'other' values or NULL stages
),
-- Final result: include wounds with either "New" or "Existing" classification and their current state
FINAL AS (
    SELECT 
        fw.woundFk,
        fw.PrimaryEtiology,
        fw.IsNew AS New,         -- 1 if the wound is "New"
        fw.IsExisting AS Existing, -- 1 if the wound is "Already Existing"
        fw.InitialAssessmentDate,
        ws.isCurrentState,
        ws.startDateDimDateFk AS CurrentStateStartDate,
        wstt.name AS CurrentStateName,  -- Corrected column reference
        hw.DaysToHeal,  -- New column for how long it took to heal
        CASE 
            WHEN hw.DaysToHeal IS NOT NULL THEN 
                CASE 
                    WHEN hw.DaysToHeal <= 90 THEN 'Before 3 months'
                    WHEN hw.DaysToHeal > 90 THEN 'After 3 months'
                END
            ELSE NULL
        END AS StateComparison,
        MIN(fps.StageValue) AS initialStage  -- Get the initial stage
    FROM 
        FilteredWounds fw
    LEFT JOIN 
        rpt.WoundState ws
        ON fw.woundFk = ws.woundFk AND ws.isCurrentState = 1
    LEFT JOIN 
        rpt.WoundStateType wstt
        ON ws.woundStateTypeFk = wstt.id
    LEFT JOIN 
        HealedWounds hw
        ON fw.woundFk = hw.woundId
    LEFT JOIN 
        FilteredPressureStages fps 
        ON fw.woundFk = fps.woundFk
    WHERE 
        fw.IsNew = 1 OR fw.IsExisting = 1
    GROUP BY 
        fw.woundFk, fw.PrimaryEtiology, fw.IsNew, fw.IsExisting, fw.InitialAssessmentDate, ws.isCurrentState, ws.startDateDimDateFk, wstt.name, hw.DaysToHeal
)
SELECT * 
FROM FINAL f 
WHERE f.StateComparison IS NOT NULL
AND f.primaryetiology='pressure'
ORDER BY f.woundFk;

    FROM rpt.Note n
    INNER JOIN rpt.AttributeType atr
        ON n.attributeTypeFk = atr.id
    INNER JOIN rpt.Wound w
        ON n.woundFk = w.id
    WHERE atr.name = 'Pressure Injury/Pressure Ulcer'
),

FilteredPressureStages AS (
    SELECT 
        ds.woundFk,
        ds.AssociatedValue AS StageValue,
        ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY ds.woundFk ORDER BY ds.Date ASC) AS MinStageRowNum,  -- Row number for minimum (earliest) stage
        ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY ds.woundFk ORDER BY ds.Date DESC) AS MaxStageRowNum  -- Row number for maximum (most recent) stage
    FROM DateSortedStages ds
    INNER JOIN FilteredWounds fw
        ON ds.woundFk = fw.wound
    WHERE (fw.IsNew = 1 OR fw.IsExisting = 1) -- Include only new or existing wounds
      AND ds.AssociatedValue IS NOT NULL  -- Exclude 'other' values or NULL stages
),

WoundCurrentState AS (
    SELECT
        ws.woundFk,
        wst.name AS currentState,  -- Get the current state from the woundstatetype table
        ws.startdate AS healedDate  -- Get the date when the wound entered the 'Resurfaced/resolved' state
    FROM rpt.woundstate ws
    INNER JOIN rpt.woundstatetype wst
        ON ws.woundstatetypefk = wst.id
    WHERE ws.isCurrentState = 1  -- Only consider the current wound state
      AND wst.name = 'Resurfaced/resolved'  -- Only consider healed wounds
)

SELECT 
    fw.wound AS woundFk,
    fw.primaryEtiology,
    fw.IsNew,
    fw.IsExisting,
    MIN(fps.StageValue) AS minimumStage,  -- Get the minimum (earliest) stage
    CASE
        WHEN wcs.currentState = 'Resurfaced/resolved' THEN 'Resurfaced/resolved'  -- Check if wound state is 'resurfaced/resolved'
        ELSE MAX(fps.StageValue)   -- Otherwise, get the maximum (most recent) stage
    END AS maximumStage,  -- Get the maximum (most recent) stage or 'Resurfaced/Resolved'
    CASE
        WHEN wcs.currentState = 'Resurfaced/resolved' THEN 1  -- Set to 1 if current state is 'Healed'
        ELSE 0  -- Otherwise, set to 0
    END AS Healed,  -- Add the Healed column with 1 or 0
    DATEDIFF(DAY, fw.InitialAssessmentDate, wcs.healedDate) AS healingDuration,  -- Calculate healing duration in days
    CASE
        WHEN DATEDIFF(DAY, fw.InitialAssessmentDate, wcs.healedDate) < 90 THEN 'Before 3 months'  -- If healing took less than 3 months
        ELSE 'After 3 months'  -- Otherwise, after 3 months
    END AS HealingBucket  -- Categorize into healing buckets
FROM FilteredWounds fw
LEFT JOIN FilteredPressureStages fps 
    ON fw.wound = fps.woundFk
LEFT JOIN WoundCurrentState wcs
    ON fw.wound = wcs.woundFk  -- Join with current state
WHERE fw.primaryEtiology = 'Pressure'
AND fps.StageValue IS NOT NULL
AND wcs.currentState = 'Resurfaced/resolved'  -- Only include wounds that are healed
GROUP BY fw.wound, fw.primaryEtiology, fw.IsNew, fw.IsExisting, wcs.currentState, fw.InitialAssessmentDate, wcs.healedDate
ORDER BY healingDuration;
